EndpointArn.Description: The Amazon Resource Number (ARN) of the endpoint being updated.

DesiredModelArn.Description: The ARN of the new model to use when updating an existing endpoint.

DesiredInferenceUnits.Description: The desired number of inference units to be used by the model using this endpoint. Each inference unit represents of a throughput of 100 characters per second.

DesiredDataAccessRoleArn.Description: Data access role ARN to use in case the new model is encrypted with a customer CMK.

Filter.Description: Filters the jobs that are returned. Jobs can be filtered on their name, status, or the date and time that they were submitted. You can set only one filter at a time.

PaginationConfig.Description: A dictionary that provides parameters to control pagination.
